Notwithstanding anything to the contrary contained in this Act or any other law—
(a) no customs or excise duty shall be charged, levied, collected or paid in respect of any goods imported into, or manufactured or produced within, Zambia by or in the name of or on behalf of the Publishing House ;
no customs or excise duty shall be charged, levied, collected or paid in respect of any goods imported into, or manufactured or produced within, Zambia by or in the name of or on behalf of the Publishing House ;
(b) the income of the Publishing House from whatever source shall be exempt from any tax payable under any written law for the time being in force relating to taxes on income and profits.
